channel.title: Portforwarding issues with my new laptop!
channel.description:
Ok so. I finally got the other stuff situated and now i cant portforward it im using a linksys router to get internet to my laptop.
Ok, I followed the linksys portforwarding guide and i tried everything First when i go into my command prompt and type 'ipconfig' it says 'javac' is not recognized as a command or some shit like that. And then when i type in the ip iget at ipchicken.com i it doesnt even work...
Someone please help me i have teamview so if you would like to not complicate my life :] Thank you.
